      <title>秘鲁通胀连续八个月保持在目标范围内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/peru-inflation-remains-within-target-for-eighth-straight-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周日公布的数据显示，11 月份秘鲁首都的通胀率连续第八个月保持在央行的目标区间内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/peru-inflation-remains-within-target-for-eighth-straight-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 15:31:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>权威机构接管比特币，带来一系列新风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/the-establishment-takeover-of-bitcoin-creates-new-list-of-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币交易所交易基金在美国取得了巨大成功，目前持有的比特币代币数量已超过 100 万枚，约占现有代币数量的 5%。这与市场第一大富豪钱包中长期冻结的比特币数量大致相同：比特币的创造者是匿名且神秘的中本聪 (Satoshi Nakamoto)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/the-establishment-takeover-of-bitcoin-creates-new-list-of-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普回归，股票与债券的两难境地困扰新兴市场投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/stocks-versus-bonds-dilemma-hits-em-investors-as-trump-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者正在争先恐后地判断唐纳德·特朗普即将重返白宫，这是否会维持或破坏乔·拜登执政期间新兴市场债券的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/stocks-versus-bonds-dilemma-hits-em-investors-as-trump-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风暴和罢工过后美国就业增长有望迅速回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/us-job-growth-due-for-snapback-after-storms-and-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在飓风和大规模罢工削弱了上个月的就业增长之后，美国 11 月份的招聘人数可能出现增长，这与劳动力市场健康但逐渐降温的状况相一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/us-job-growth-due-for-snapback-after-storms-and-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
